itemList.name: Keep trying
itemList.text: If at first you don't succeed, skydiving is not for you!

itemList.name: The way to fish
itemList.text: Give a man a fish and he will eat for a day. Teach him how to fish and he will sit in a boat and drink beer all day.

itemList.name: Know your limits
itemList.text: You know you're getting old when your wife says, "Honey, lets run upstairs and make love," and you answer, "I can't do both."

itemList.name: Sand
itemList.text: What do you have when 100 lawyers are buried up to their necks in sand? Not enough sand.

itemList.name: Dating
itemList.text: When Magnesium and Oxygen started dating I was like, "O MG!"
